<inglise> Conditions for a Community contribution to risk capital </inglise>
<eesti> Tingimused &uuml;henduse osalemiseks riskikapitalis </eesti>
<inglise> Applications for financial assistance under Article 4(1) (e) of the Regulation shall include the following information, satisfactory to the Committee referred to in Article 17 thereof, as a basis for decisions to grant assistance: </inglise>
<eesti> Finantsabi taotlused vastavalt k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 1 punktile e sisaldavad j&auml;rgmist teavet, mida artiklis 17 nimetatud komitee peab vajalikuks abi andmise otsuse alusena: </eesti>
<inglise> - an information memorandum containing the main provisions of the statutory documentation of the fund including its legal and management structure, </inglise>
<eesti> - teabekiri, mis sisaldab fondi kohustuslike dokumentide p&otilde;his&auml;tteid, kaasa arvatud tema &otilde;iguslik ja haldusstruktuur, </eesti>
<inglise> - its detailed investment guidelines including information on target projects, </inglise>
<eesti> - fondi &uuml;ksikasjalikud investeerimissuunised, kaasa arvatud andmed sihtprojektide kohta, </eesti>
<inglise> - information on the involvement of private investors, </inglise>
<eesti> - teave erainvesteerijate osaluse kohta, </eesti>
<inglise> - information on geographical coverage, </inglise>
<eesti> - teave geograafilise ulatuse kohta, </eesti>
<inglise> - information on the financial viability of the fund, </inglise>
<eesti> - teave fondi rahandusliku eluj&otilde;ulisuse kohta, </eesti>
<inglise> - information on the rights of the investors to take remedial action in the event that the undertakings given to them are not honoured by the fund, </inglise>
<eesti> - teave investorite &otilde;iguste kohta kasutada &otilde;iguskaitsevahendeid juhul, kui fond ei j&auml;rgi neile antud kohustusi, </eesti>
<inglise> - information on the exit policies of the fund and arrangements for the termination of the fund, </inglise>
<eesti> - teave fondi v&auml;ljaastumise kohta ja fondi l&otilde;petamise kord, </eesti>
<inglise> - rights of representation in the committees of investors. </inglise>
<eesti> - esindus&otilde;igus investorite komiteedes. </eesti>
<inglise> Before the decision to grant assistance, the intermediary investment fund or other comparable financial institution must undertake to invest not less than a sum equivalent to two and a half times the Community contribution, into projects previously identified as projects of common interest in accordance with Article 155(1) first subparagraph, first indent of the Treaty. </inglise>
<eesti> Enne abi andmise otsust peab vahendav investeerimisfond v&otilde;i muu asjakohane finantsasutus kohustuma investeerima &uuml;henduse osast v&auml;hemalt kaks ja pool korda suurema summa projektidesse, mis on varem kindlaks m&auml;&auml;ratud &uuml;hist huvi pakkuvate projektidena vastavalt asutamislepingu artikli 155 l&otilde;ike 1 esimese l&otilde;igu esimesele taandele. </eesti>
<inglise> Community aid for investment funds or comparable financial undertakings, if granted in the form of a risk-capital participation, shall be granted, in principle, only if the Community contribution ranks pari passu in terms of risk with other investors in the fund. </inglise>
<eesti> Riskikapitali osaluse vormis antavat &uuml;henduse abi investeerimisfondidele v&otilde;i asjakohastele finantsasutustele antakse &uuml;ldiselt ainult juhul, kui &uuml;henduse osa on riski osas samav&auml;&auml;rne teiste fondi investorite omaga. </eesti>
<inglise> Recipient investment funds or comparable financial undertakings have to follow sound financial principles. </inglise>
<eesti> Abi saavad investeerimisfondid v&otilde;i asjakohased finantsasutused peavad j&auml;rgima usaldusv&auml;&auml;rse finantsjuhtimise p&otilde;him&otilde;tteid. </eesti>
