<inglise> Management of the Community contribution </inglise>
<eesti> &Uuml;henduse osaluse haldamine </eesti>
<inglise> The management of the Community contribution will be ensured by the European Investment Fund (EIF). </inglise>
<eesti> &Uuml;henduse osaluse haldamise tagab Euroopa Investeerimisfond (EIF). </eesti>
<inglise> The detailed terms and conditions for implementing Community assistance under Article 4(1) (e) of the Regulation, including its monitoring and control, shall be laid down in a Cooperation Agreement between the Commission and the EIF, taking into account the provisions laid down in this Annex. </inglise>
<eesti> &Uuml;ksikasjalikud tingimused &uuml;henduse abi rakendamiseks vastavalt k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 1 punktile e, kaasa arvatud selle j&auml;lgimiseks ja kontrolliks, s&auml;testatakse koost&ouml;&ouml;lepingus komisjoni ja EIF vahel, v&otilde;ttes arvesse k&auml;esoleva lisa s&auml;tteid. </eesti>
<inglise> 4. </inglise>
