<inglise> Other provisions </inglise>
<eesti> Muud s&auml;tted </eesti>
<inglise> The provisions applying to appraisal, monitoring and evaluation as specified in the Regulation shall apply in full to Article 4(1) (e) thereof, including the provisions on conditions for Community aid, on financial control and the reduction, suspension and cancellation of assistance. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses t&auml;psustatud s&auml;tteid eelhindamise, j&auml;relevalve ja hindamise kohta kohaldatakse t&auml;ielikult m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti e suhtes, kaasa arvatud s&auml;tted &uuml;henduse abi tingimuste, finantskontrolli ning abi v&auml;hendamise, peatamise ja t&uuml;histamise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise> This shall, inter alia, be ensured by appropriate provisions in the Cooperation Agreement between the Commission and the EIF and appropriate agreements with investee funds or comparable financial undertakings stipulating the necessary controls at the level of individual projects of common interest. </inglise>
<eesti> Muu hulgas tagatakse see vastavate s&auml;tetega komisjoni ja EIF vahelises koost&ouml;&ouml;lepingus ja sobivate kokkulepetega investeerimisfondide v&otilde;i asjakohaste finantsasutustega, mis n&auml;evad ette vajalikud kontrollimised individuaalsete &uuml;hist huvi pakkuvate projektide puhul. </eesti>
<inglise> Appropriate arrangements will be made to allow the Court of Auditors to exercise its mission in particular in order to verify the regularity of payments made. </inglise>
<eesti> V&otilde;etakse vastu asjakohased korraldused, mis v&otilde;imaldavad Euroopa Kontrollikojal oma &uuml;lesannet t&auml;ita, eelk&otilde;ige t&otilde;estada tehtud maksete korrap&auml;rasust. </eesti>
<inglise> Payments under Article 4(1) (e) shall be governed by Article 11(7) thereof, notwithstanding Article 11(6) thereof. </inglise>
<eesti> Artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti e kohaseid makseid reguleerib artikli 11 l&otilde;ige 7, piiramata artikli 11 l&otilde;ike 6 kohaldamist. </eesti>
<inglise> After the end of the investment period or earlier as the case may be, any balances resulting from a return of invested capital or distribution of profits and capital gains and any and all other distributions due to investors shall be returned to the Community budget. </inglise>
<eesti> P&auml;rast investeerimisperioodi l&otilde;ppu v&otilde;i v&otilde;imaluse korral varem tagastatakse &uuml;henduse eelarvesse k&otilde;ik investeeritud kapitali tulu v&otilde;i kasumi jaotamisest, samuti kapitali kasvutulude ning k&otilde;igi muude investoritele makstavate osade saldod. </eesti>
<inglise> All decisions to provide risk-capital participations under Article 4(1) (e) of the Regulation shall be submitted to the Committee referred to in Article 17 thereof. </inglise>
<eesti> K&otilde;ik otsused pakkuda riskikapitali osalust vastavalt artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 1 punktile e esitatakse artiklis 17 nimetatud komiteele. </eesti>
<inglise> The Commission will report regularly to the said Committee on the implementation of risk capital participations under Article 4(1) (e) of the Regulation. </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjon teatab nimetatud komiteele korrap&auml;raselt k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti e kohasest riskikapitali osaluste rakendamisest. </eesti>
<inglise> Before the end of 2006, the Commission shall in the framework of Article 15 of the Regulation provide an evaluation of actions carried out under Article 4(1) (e) thereof, in particular on its utilisation, its effects on the implementation of the trans-European network projects supported and the involvement of private investors in the projects financed." </inglise>
<eesti> Enne 2006. aasta l&otilde;ppu esitab komisjon k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 15 raames hinnangu artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti e kohaselt tehtule, eriti selle kasutamisele, selle m&otilde;jule toetatavate &uuml;leeuroopaliste v&otilde;rguprojektide rakendamiseks ja erainvestorite osalemiseks rahastatud projektides." </eesti>
 